
# Function


## ```js parseRgba ```


Parse RGBA string and return an object

## Parameters

- **rgbaString**  String: The rgba string (rgba(r,g,b,a)) to parse



## Example (js)

```js
import parseRgba from '@coffeekraken/sugar/js/color/parseRgba';
parseRgba('rgba(20,10,100,20)');
```
